  <name>Reco</name>
  <summary>Convert between lower case and upper case in your text</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A small text tool app that allows you convert case in the text view.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Click "Copy to Clipboard" button to copy the all texts in the text view without selecting them</li>
      <li>Undo and redo for case changes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
